    "description": "《Mosey the Pirate》是飞天意面神怪物(Flying Spaghetti Monster)官方动作冒险游戏，游戏主角是莫西，一名来自飞天意面神教的海盗！跟随莫西踏上它的人生冒险之旅，从一个夜班经理菲尔手下卑微的快餐厨师成为世界上第一个海盗，飞天意面神怪物最神圣、最令人恐惧的天选之人。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704700/extras/543dcf9d50bee3ccc3388a0e130ac04f.poster.avif?t=1728630827\" width=616 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704700/extras/543dcf9d50bee3ccc3388a0e130ac04f.webm?t=1728630827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704700/extras/543dcf9d50bee3ccc3388a0e130ac04f.mp4?t=1728630827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >递过啤酒!</h2>探索一个如真实一般的开放古代世界!好吧，你说对了。它实际上是古代、现代和海盗的黄金时代的混合体！但有一件事我们可以保证——你从来没有见过这样的场景！它拥有各种不同的活动，比如:<br>•稳稳的贴浪平航！<br>•收集战利品！<br>•面食烹饪！<br>•虚张声势的战斗！<br>•让人挠头的解谜！<br>•甚至可以让你飞的小机械发明！<br>•感叹号！还有更多！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704700/extras/09bf7f556bdb1c66b0e27900f9806815.poster.avif?t=1728630827\" width=616 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704700/extras/09bf7f556bdb1c66b0e27900f9806815.webm?t=1728630827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704700/extras/09bf7f556bdb1c66b0e27900f9806815.mp4?t=1728630827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不要脱轨！</h2>通过一个滑稽夸张的故事情节，解释了“飞天意面神怪物”这个令人恐惧的词是如何第一次传遍世界的:<br>•见证莫西的冒险生活！<br>•让地中海的好人们知道飞天意面神怪物！和他们一起共饮啤酒！他们太酷了！<br>•显然不是所有人都很酷！都怪我们！帮助莫西船长和他的船员征服一些不知道如何反击的敌人！<br>•人都有问题，难道你不知道！像一个真正的海盗一样帮助他们！也许他们真的会感激改变，但不要指望这样！<br>•访问埃及、希腊、罗马、地中海所有的旅游热点城市，而无需离开你的电脑椅半步！这样非常懒，但我们有什么资格去评判呢?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704700/extras/5634b7780659c9ccbadc88668ac3e103.poster.avif?t=1728630827\" width=616 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704700/extras/5634b7780659c9ccbadc88668ac3e103.webm?t=1728630827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704700/extras/5634b7780659c9ccbadc88668ac3e103.mp4?t=1728630827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >面条故事！</h2>还有通心粉双关语等等！<br>.．.<br>不，真的。这一点就到此为止。或者我应该说，我们是意大利面。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704700/extras/6d98c35c0fbe61d01e02339b682d8bc2.poster.avif?t=1728630827\" width=616 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704700/extras/6d98c35c0fbe61d01e02339b682d8bc2.webm?t=1728630827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704700/extras/6d98c35c0fbe61d01e02339b682d8bc2.mp4?t=1728630827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >圣杯?</h2>收集一系列惊艳的海盗勋章！提升莫西技能的物品，证明他的实力，在整个游戏中管理他的技能:<br>•收集武器，无论是近战还是远程：剑、军刀、投石器、手枪、步枪和海盗的奥尔的重机枪-意大利面过滤器！<br>•手套，让你爬上最高的悬崖！<br>•滑翔机，让你翱翔在最高的天空！<br>•海盗帽子！这些，呃，这些只是让你看起来时髦，让我们面对现实吧——这是现代游戏;没有帽子可不行。<br>•一把长柄勺和其他器皿！一决高下！<br>•一个RPG般的系统，你的海盗的技能管理！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704700/extras/1178ad2dd21bf36162dcd10cf39c6500.poster.avif?t=1728630827\" width=616 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704700/extras/1178ad2dd21bf36162dcd10cf39c6500.webm?t=1728630827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704700/extras/1178ad2dd21bf36162dcd10cf39c6500.mp4?t=1728630827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >启航！</h2>建造并维护一艘属于你自己并且适合航海的船——强大的意大利千层面！<br>•雇佣一名船员！<br>•管理船上的补给！<br>•通过迷你游戏修复伤害！<br>•进行凶猛的海战！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704700/extras/8c69064d2926955e1668989e092dbaac.poster.avif?t=1728630827\" width=616 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704700/extras/8c69064d2926955e1668989e092dbaac.webm?t=1728630827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704700/extras/8c69064d2926955e1668989e092dbaac.mp4?t=1728630827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>这就是你的海盗生活，只要你响应召唤！起锚，把意大利面拉紧！是时候开始一段一生难忘的旅程了！R'amen！</strong>",
